  "text": "Firefox's Servo-based CSS style system in layout/style/ is composed of the following core files:\n\n1. **ServoStyleSet** (header + source): `layout/style/ServoStyleSet.h` and `layout/style/ServoStyleSet.cpp` — The class `ServoStyleSet` is the main entry point for style resolution. It is backed by a Servo Stylist and manages the set of StyleSheets that apply to a document. It is a friend of `RestyleManager` and exposes methods for resolving styles, evaluating source size lists, and managing post-traversal tasks. The static member `sInServoTraversal` tracks whether a Servo traversal is in progress.\n\n2. **ServoBindings** (header): `layout/style/ServoBindings.h` — Declares the Gecko-to-Servo FFI (Foreign Function Interface) functions. These are C-linkage functions prefixed with `Servo_` (e.g., `Servo_StyleSet_StyleRuleChanged`, `Servo_CssRules_GetStyleRuleAt`) generated via macros like `BASIC_RULE_FUNCS_LOCKED` and `GROUP_RULE_FUNCS_UNLOCKED`. The file comment explicitly states: 'FFI functions for Gecko to call into Servo'.\n\n3. **RestyleManager** (header): `layout/style/RestyleManager.h` — The class `RestyleManager` schedules and manages style recalculation. It is a friend of `dom::Document` and `ServoStyleSet`. Key methods include `ProcessPendingRestyles()`, `PostRestyleEvent()`, `RebuildAllStyleData()`, `ProcessRestyledFrames()`, and `ProcessPostTraversal()`. It also defines the helper class `ServoRestyleState` used to pass restyle state during traversal.\n\n4. **ServoUtils** (header): `layout/style/ServoUtils.h` — Provides utility functions for Servo traversal state. Key declarations include `IsInServoTraversal()` (an inline function checking the `sInServoTraversal` pointer), `InitializeServo()`, `ShutdownServo()`, and `AssertIsMainThreadOrServoFontMetricsLocked()`.\n\n5. **moz.build**: `layout/style/moz.build` — The Mozilla build configuration file for `layout/style/`. It lists all style system source files under `UNIFIED_SOURCES` (e.g., `ServoStyleSet.cpp`, `RestyleManager.cpp`, `GeckoBindings.cpp`, and ~80 other .cpp files) and all exported headers under `EXPORTS.mozilla` (including `ServoStyleSet.h`, `ServoBindings.h`, `RestyleManager.h`, `ServoUtils.h`, etc.). It also configures generated files like `ServoStyleConsts.h` (via cbindgen from Rust) and `ServoCSSPropList.h`."
